{"tid":311708,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Tesla收瀉5%陷熊　恐預示股市狂歡水尾 (04:37)","createTime":"2017-07-07T00:18:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-08T07:39:50.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"22cc6e1b02a229b3602d2693bcc7f4997a5fc996","tid":311708,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T00:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170707/img/20170707043724fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170707%2Fimg%2F20170707043724fi_p1.jpg&h=28b830ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=eufLZs2OTZj7nUe3CMdYifM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=bc799c77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】美國電動車生產商特斯拉(Tesla)頭頭碰着黑！繼近日公布第2季付運量遜預期後，周三遭高盛唱淡，將6個月目標價由190美元削至180美元，較現價有40%下跌空間，又爆出內部性騷擾醜聞，股價已於周三急插7.2%，為去年6月以來最傷。惟噩運未完，沽空機構香櫞(Citron Research)隨即表明，認同高盛睇淡，並已即時再沽空Tesla。<br />\n<br />\nTesla股價周四續跌，收報308.89美元，再瀉5.56%，最低曾見306.3美元，插6.36%，計及周一跌2.4%及周三挫7.2%，已連瀉3日累挫15%，更由6月高峰累瀉20%，技術上陷入「熊市」，公司市值亦大減至約510億美元，終被通用汽車(GM)重新超越，失落全美國最高市值汽車企業地位。外電報道，Tesla連瀉3日，淡友終於能狂賺超過10億美元，但仍未能補償之前損失。<br />\n<br />\n美國資深汽車業投資評論員Matthew DeBord曾警告，「特斯拉泡沫」十分明顯，基本因素根本不能支持股價！DeBord指出，特斯拉股價如果要在300美元水平徘徊，在2020年時，銷量需要高達100萬輛，但產能遠遠不及，明顯有重大泡沫，早前不斷上升只是「挾淡倉」造成，估計淡友狂輸逾30億美元。他又指出，Tesla可能是今次牛市的「最後瘋狂」，為股市泡沫指標。<br />\n<br />\n香櫞創辦人Andrew Left亦透露，在美股臨收市前再沽更多Tesla股份，因估計Tesla電動車銷量低，以及在SUV市場將見愈來愈多競爭者。他並稱，在沒有競爭對手的情況下，Tesla都輸錢，何況在有競爭的時候？他形容，每輛Tesla都是蝕本貨，所以買Tesla股份的投資者只在賭一個願景。他提醒投資者在300美元買入Tesla是不明智。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170707/20170707043724fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170707%2F20170707043724fi.html&d=eufLZs2OTZj7nUe3CMdYifM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=35b59c57\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170707/20170707043724fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"6776fb1eedc79f2335696124a3c3d65cc76db92d","tid":311708,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:23:40.000Z","msg":"梁國雄議員..."},{"pid":"387686716cb344d465ef1b6c92d77a6b35ad3dca","tid":311708,"uid":66157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:28:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梁國雄議員...</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20170707/photo/bkn-20170707043723607-0707_00842_001_02b.jpg?20170707043733\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20170707%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170707043723607-0707_00842_001_02b.jpg%3F20170707043733&h=bcc446e7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5781c54722fde27374a7f0be55044e0f1ebb03ff","tid":311708,"uid":119937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T03:14:01.000Z","msg":"molamola 我架model s 跌價la"},{"pid":"72b4d008789bc7dd0c12d327478bf234a081bc93","tid":311708,"uid":22585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T05:12:01.000Z","msg":"高盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce92c0b49a32ae7e8600d6a2308a299138344dd3","tid":311708,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高盛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973a5cb84e2d7fb7a2f8d1ec18f2884345c6830f","tid":311708,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T07:39:50.000Z","msg":"Andrew Left 今次沽空幾多Tsla<br />\n上次沽空恒大贏得160萬，仲要比證監告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}